00:41:09.870 --> 00:41:11.420
Get in on the conversation.

00:41:11.420 --> 00:41:12.420
You should want to know.

00:41:12.420 --> 00:41:15.180
And so you should always be
asking, how can I do better?

00:41:15.180 --> 00:41:16.680
What am I doing
that frustrates you?

00:41:16.680 --> 00:41:17.490
What can I improve?

00:41:17.490 --> 00:41:21.240
If you just ask
for the feedback--

00:41:21.240 --> 00:41:24.280
and don't wait
until it's too late.

00:41:24.280 --> 00:41:25.502
