00:43:50.230 --> 00:43:51.680
It's bad.

00:43:51.680 --> 00:43:53.260
The industry has become this--

00:43:53.260 --> 00:43:53.990
it's terrible.

00:43:53.990 --> 00:43:56.020
There's people out there
just dispensing advice

00:43:56.020 --> 00:43:58.145
because someone told them--
their mother told them,

00:43:58.145 --> 00:43:59.904
you're so smart!

00:43:59.904 --> 00:44:02.070
So make sure somebody has
got some clinical training

00:44:02.070 --> 00:44:03.569
and some behavioral
science training

00:44:03.569 --> 00:44:06.346
and knows what they're
coaching you in.

00:44:06.346 --> 00:44:08.140
And get feedback.

00:44:08.140 --> 00:44:12.230
I hired a coach two
years ago for me.

00:44:12.230 --> 00:44:14.355
And people were like, at
this point in your career?

00:44:14.355 --> 00:44:16.090
You probably think
it's too late.

00:44:16.090 --> 00:44:17.140
But it's never too late.

00:44:17.140 --> 00:44:19.450
And all I have
thought for two years

00:44:19.450 --> 00:44:21.970
was, why did I wait so long?

00:44:21.970 --> 00:44:23.790
Help is so good.

00:44:23.790 --> 00:44:25.900
I mean, none of us
can do this alone.

00:44:25.900 --> 00:44:31.220
And if you think you can,
please don't lead anybody.

00:44:31.220 --> 00:44:34.780
So the idea of getting help,
and having somebody-- we

00:44:34.780 --> 00:44:37.210
are notoriously bad
observers of our own reality.

00:44:37.210 --> 00:44:38.890
We don't have good third eyes.

00:44:38.890 --> 00:44:40.510
So having another
set of eyes on you

00:44:40.510 --> 00:44:41.885
and how you function
in the world

00:44:41.885 --> 00:44:44.950
and how others experience you,
even if you have people getting

00:44:44.950 --> 00:44:46.690
in your face and
being honest, still,

00:44:46.690 --> 00:44:48.810
to have an objective
third party tell you,

00:44:48.810 --> 00:44:50.350
here's who you are to the world.

00:44:50.350 --> 00:44:51.770
Now, if that's not what you
want to be to the world,

00:44:51.770 --> 00:44:53.061
here's how you can change that.

00:44:53.061 --> 00:44:54.010
What a gift!

00:44:54.010 --> 00:44:57.151
And the earlier you
do it, the better.

00:44:57.151 --> 00:44:59.400
I tell every one of my clients
who run big departments

00:44:59.400 --> 00:45:01.470
