coach, and I want

00:45:03.640 --> 00:45:06.760
the name of your therapist,
your personal trainer,

00:45:06.760 --> 00:45:09.166
and your nutritionist.

00:45:09.166 --> 00:45:10.880
There's a foursome there.

00:45:10.880 --> 00:45:12.910
You should not be
running tens of thousands

00:45:12.910 --> 00:45:14.410
of people and
billions of dollars

00:45:14.410 --> 00:45:18.410
of budgets without at least,
if not more, those four things

00:45:18.410 --> 00:45:18.910
around you.

