00:46:28.670 --> 00:46:31.707
The problem becomes after you're
trying to fight that, right?

00:46:31.707 --> 00:46:34.040
So if you're trying to introduce
better decision-making,

00:46:34.040 --> 00:46:35.790
because you're good
at it and they're not,

00:46:35.790 --> 00:46:39.620
or you're trying to bridge
the seams and you get resisted

00:46:39.620 --> 00:46:43.887
and no one else is on that same
mission, you fail, but slower.

